msgid ""
"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Los pagos con Stripe Crypto (USDC) están DISPONIBLES SOLO para negocios con "
"sede en EE. UU. Si te encuentras fuera de EE. UU., Stripe solo aceptará "
"pagos con tarjeta de crédito a tu saldo de Stripe (no directamente a "
"cripto)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Si estás en EE. UU., puedes usar Stripe para recibir cripto directamente. Si"
" estás fuera, considera NOWPayments o CoinGate para pagos directos de "
"cripto."

